      • visitOrProbe

        public final void visitOrProbe(@Nullable
                               org.eclipse.core.resources.IResourceDelta delta,
                               @Nullable
                               org.eclipse.core.resources.IResource resource)
        Deprecated. 
        Resolves supplied resource delta or resource of a change event. If the resource delta is not null then this method visits it, otherwise it probes the specified resource.

        This method always invokes preVisitOrProbe() before resolving specified arguments but invokes postVisitOrProbe() only after successful resolving (post hook is not invoked in case of an exception).

        Throws:
        RuntimeCoreException - if the visit or probe fail for some reason
